components.content: The experiment showed that hypothesis 2 is not correct.
Here are some facts to help:
Lucy has trees on her farm that she can use to build hives.
Lucy will have to remove some corn crops to add cotton crops.
Add beehives around the corn crops. The elephants will see the beehives and be scared away.
Plant cotton crops around the corn crops to attract bees. The bees will scare away the elephants.
Explain how the cotton experiment supports your hypothesis.
